'5 points', '6 points', '7 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2hpi')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2hpi" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>On the nature of ethics:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>There is no justice in the laws of Nature, Headmaster, no term for fairness in the equations of motion. The universe is neither evil, nor good, it simply does not care. The stars don't care, or the Sun, or the sky. But they don't have to! <em>We</em> care! There is light in the world, and it is <em>us</em>.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>~ Eliezer Yudkowsky c/o Harry Potter, Methods of Rationality chapter 39.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2hpi"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2hpi" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2hpi')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2hpi" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2hpi')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2hpi" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2jj/rationality_quotes_august_2010/2hpi?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2hpi" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2hpi')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2hpi class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2hpi" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2gz7" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2gz7" class="parent"><a name="2gz7" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2gz7" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2gz7" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2gz7" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">19 August 2010 01:55:32PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >5 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2gz7'] = ['4 points', '5 points', '6 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2gz7')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2gz7" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2gz7" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">19 August 2010 01:55:32PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2gz7'>5 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2gz7'] = ['4 points', '5 points', '6 points