/javascript">vl['t1_2d1n'] = ['11 points', '12 points', '13 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2d1n')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2d1n" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>Read, every day, something no one else is reading. Think, every day, something no one else is thinking. Do, every day, something no one else would be silly enough to do. It is bad for the mind to be always part of unanimity.</p>
</blockquote>

