id="reply_a_t1_2d4k" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2d4k')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2d4k class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2d4k" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2d4k" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2d4k" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2ds2" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2ds2" class="parent"><a name="2ds2" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2ds2" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2ds2" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2ds2" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 August 2010 08:31:55AM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2ds2'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2ds2')">[+] (2 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2ds2" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2ds2" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 August 2010 08:31:55AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2ds2'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2ds2'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2ds2')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2ds2" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Wouldn't a good summary of rationality be a little more comprehensible? I'm sure there is a deep insight that Nic sees behind the quote and from what you say it must be related to rationality but at face value, without context that most people, myself included, don't have it makes no sense.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2ds2"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2ds2" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2ds2')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2ds2" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2ds2')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2ds2" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2jj/rationality_quotes_august_2010/2ds2?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2ds2" href="#2d4k" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2ds2" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2ds2')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2ds2 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2ds2" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2ds2" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2ds2" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2dv1" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2dv1" class="parent"><a name="2dv1" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2dv1" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2dv1" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2dv1" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Nic_Smith/">Nic_Smith</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 August 2010 10:19:47PM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2dv1'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2dv1')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2dv1" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2dv1" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Nic_Smith/">Nic_Smith</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 August 2010 10:19:47PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2dv1'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2dv1'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2dv1')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2dv1" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Wow, I had no idea that this quote would be so controversial. I will attempt to explain.</p>

<p>To begin, I think there is something that can be learned from the quote, but I wouldn't call it a "deep insight." Or, at least, I wouldn't have before uninverted's reply. Silence, a friend of mine, was making fun of the focus of many anime on literal, physical strength, often detached from <a href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/nb/something_to_protect/">anything to protect</a> or, indeed, any real overall goal at all (I don't remember if this is the case with <em>Prism Ark</em> or not). It's thus a <em>light</em> warning against focusing too much on method over end results.</p>

<p>Also, if there were two of you, it'd be impossible for you[a] to be decisively stronger and more skilled than you[b].</p>

<p>Uninverted, I'm guessing, was thinking of akrasia and overcoming cognitive biases, which can be considered "part of self" and, at the same time, something to "defeat" as easily as possible. Hence, the quote can also be read as a summary of rationality.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2dv1"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2dv1" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2dv1')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2dv1" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2dv1')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2dv1" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2jj/rationality_quotes_august_2010/2dv1?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2dv1" href="#2ds2" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2dv1" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2dv1')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2dv1 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2dv1" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2dv1" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2dv1" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2e2r" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2e2r" class="parent"><a name="2e2r" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2e2r" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2e2r" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2e2r" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/uninverted/">uninverted</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">09 August 2010 07:35:43AM</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2e2r'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2e2r')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2e2r" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2e2r" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/uninverted/">uninverted</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">09 August 2010 07:35:43AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2e2r'>0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2e2r'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2e2r')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2e2r" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Yes, that's what I thought exactly.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2e2r"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2e2r" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2e2r')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2e2r" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2e2r')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2e2r" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2jj/rationality_quotes_august_2010/2e2r?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2e2r" href="#2dv1" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2e2r" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2e2r')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2e2r class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2e2r" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2d59" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2d59" class="parent"><a name="2d59" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2d59" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2d59" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2d59" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/sketerpot/">sketerpot</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">03 August 2010 10:33:34PM</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2d59'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2d59')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2d59" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2d59" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/sketerpot/">sketerpot</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">03 August 2010 10:33:34PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2d59'>0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2d59'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2d59')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2d59" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>With a big enough hammer, that goal is within the reach of anybody strong enough to swing it at their own head.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2d59"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2d59" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2d59')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2d59" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2d59')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2d59" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2jj/rationality_quotes_august_2010/2d59?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2d59" href="#2d2p" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2d59" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2d59')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2d59 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2d59" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2d0z" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2d0z" class="parent"><a name="2d0z" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2d0z" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2d0z" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2d0z" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/RichardKennaway/">RichardKennaway</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">03 August 2010 07:54:49AM</span><span class="votes " >12 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2d0z'] = ['11 points', '12 points', '13 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2d0z')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2d0z" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2d0z" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/RichardKennaway/">RichardKennaway</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">03 August 2010 07:54:49AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2d0z'>12 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2d0z'] = ['11 points', '12 points', '13 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2d0z')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2d0z" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>When I was a young man about to go out into the world, my father says to me a very valuable thing. He says to me like this... "Son," the old guy says, "I am sorry that I am not able to bank roll you to a very large start, but not having any potatoes which to give you, I am now going to stake you to some very valuable advice. One of these days in your travels, a guy is going to come to you and show you a nice, brand new deck of cards on which the seal has not yet been broken. This man is going to offer to bet you that he can make the jack of spades jump out of the deck and squirt cider in your ear. Now son, do not bet this man, for as sure as you stand there, you are going to wind up with an earful of cider."</p>
</blockquote>

<p>-- Sky Masterson, a character in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guys_and_Dolls" rel="nofollow">&quot;Guys and Dolls&quot;</a></p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2d0z"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2d0z" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2d0z')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2d0z" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2d0z')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2d0z" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2jj/rationality_quotes_august_2010/2d0z?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2d0z" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2d0z')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2d0z class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2d0z" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2d0z" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2d0z" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2d5n" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2d5n" class="parent"><a name="2d5n" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2d5n" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2d5n" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2d5n" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Psychohistorian/">Psychohistorian</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">03 August 2010 11:46:47PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2d5n'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2d5n')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2d5n" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2d5n" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Psychohistorian/">Psychohistorian</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">03 August 2010 11:46:47PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2d5n'>3 points