9i" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2h9i" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/orthonormal/">orthonormal</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">20 August 2010 05:36:00PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2h9i'>2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2h9i'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2h9i')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2h9i" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Indeed. It's <a href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/ir/science_as_attire/">Science as Attire</a> in more ways than one.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2h9i"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2h9i" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2h9i')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2h9i" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2h9i')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2h9i" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2jj/rationality_quotes_august_2010/2h9i?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2h9i" href="#2d2c" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2h9i" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2h9i')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2h9i class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2h9i" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2d4t" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2d4t" class="parent"><a name="2d4t" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2d4t" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2d4t" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2d4t" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/DSimon/">DSimon</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">03 August 2010 09:32:56PM</span><span clas